    <div class="chat-messages" id="chatMessages">
        <div class="message bot-message">
            <div class="bubble bot-bubble">
                📚 <strong>Welcome to Topic 3: Developing the Approach to the Problem!</strong><br><br>
                I'm here to help you master the critical components of marketing research approach development.<br><br>
