            <div class="suggestion-chip">How to develop hypotheses? (null vs alternative)</div>
            <div class="suggestion-chip">Why is literature review important?</div>
            <div class="suggestion-chip">Steps in conducting a literature review</div>
            <div class="suggestion-chip">APA referencing format examples</div>
            <div class="suggestion-chip">Do's and Don'ts of literature review</div>
